'''凱西·A·麥茲'''（{{lang-en|Casey A. Mize}}，{{bd|1997年|5月1日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的投手，目前效力於底特律老虎。他是2018年美國職棒大聯盟選秀的選秀狀元，並於2020年8月19日登上大聯盟。
==職業生涯==
===小聯盟===
2018年美國職棒大聯盟選秀，老虎隊將麥茲選為選秀狀元。<ref>{{cite web|title=Tigers draft Auburn right-hander Casey Mize with No. 1 pick|url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/23698270/detroit-tigers-draft-casey-mize-auburn-tigers-no-1-pick|website=ESPN.com|agency=Associated Press|date=June 5, 2018|accessdate=June 7, 2018|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129045038/https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/23698270/detroit-tigers-draft-casey-mize-auburn-tigers-no-1-pick|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在6月25日以75萬美元的合約加盟老虎隊。<ref>{{cite web|title=Tigers agree to deal with No. 1 pick Mize|url=https://www.mlb.com/tigers/news/no-1-draft-pick-casey-mize-signs-with-tigers/c-282841088|website=MLB.com|first=Jason|last=Beck|date=June 25, 2018|accessdate=June 25, 2018|archive-date=2018-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180710111322/https://www.mlb.com/tigers/news/no-1-draft-pick-casey-mize-signs-with-tigers/c-282841088|dead-url=no}}</ref>並從新人聯盟起步。2018年他在小聯盟吞下1敗，防禦率為3.95。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=663554#/career/R/pitching/2018/ALL|title=Casey Mize Stats, Highlights, Bio - MiLB.com Stats - The Official Site of Minor League Baseball|publisher=MiLB.com|accessdate=September 11, 2018|archive-date=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102043620/http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=663554#/career/R/pitching/2018/ALL|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2019，麥茲受邀參加大聯盟春訓。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.milb.com/milb/news/detroit-tigers-invite-casey-mize-to-spring-training/c-302959956 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-10-31 |archive-date=2019-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190123071446/https://www.milb.com/milb/news/detroit-tigers-invite-casey-mize-to-spring-training/c-302959956 |dead-url=no }}</ref>他在高階1A先發4場比賽，防禦率僅0.35。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.milb.com/milb/news/detroit-tigers-casey-mize-moving-up-to-double-a-erie-seawolves/c-306576304 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-10-31 |archive-date=2019-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190426202027/https://www.milb.com/milb/news/detroit-tigers-casey-mize-moving-up-to-double-a-erie-seawolves/c-306576304 |dead-url=no }}</ref>升上2A後的首場先發，麥茲便投出無安打比賽。<ref>{{cite news|first=Jeff|last=Seidel|title=No-no! Detroit Tigers' Casey Mize throws brilliant no-hitter in Double-A debut|url=https://www.freep.com/story/sports/columnists/jeff-seidel/2019/04/29/casey-mize-detroit-tigers-no-hitter-erie-double-a-debut/3621100002/|website=Detroit Free Press|date=April 29, 2019|accessdate=April 30, 2019|archive-date=2020-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201006150822/https://www.freep.com/story/sports/columnists/jeff-seidel/2019/04/29/casey-mize-detroit-tigers-no-hitter-erie-double-a-debut/3621100002/|dead-url=no}}</ref>6月15日，他因為肩膀受傷進入傷兵名單。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.freep.com/story/sports/mlb/tigers/2019/06/14/casey-mize-injury-detroit-tigers/1458875001/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-10-31 |archive-date=2020-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926155040/https://www.freep.com/story/sports/mlb/tigers/2019/06/14/casey-mize-injury-detroit-tigers/1458875001/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
===底特律老虎===
2020年8月19日，麥茲被球隊拉上大聯盟。他在初登板面對白襪隊，<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.mlb.com/tigers/news/casey-mize-tarik-skubal-called-up | title=Tigers call up top prospects Mize, Skubal | work=MLB.com | author=Jason Beck | date=August 17, 2020 | accessdate=August 19, 2020 | archive-date=2020-08-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820092311/https://www.mlb.com/tigers/news/casey-mize-tarik-skubal-called-up | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.mlb.com/tigers/news/casey-mize-strikes-out-7-in-mlb-debut | title=A-Mize-ing! Casey fans 7, walks 0 in debut | work=MLB.com | author=Jason Beck | date=August 19, 2020 | accessdate=August 20, 2020 | archive-date=2020-08-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820092303/https://www.mlb.com/tigers/news/casey-mize-strikes-out-7-in-mlb-debut | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.mlb.com/tigers/news/casey-mize-dane-dunning-debut-history | title=Mize, Dunning make history in debut face off | work=MLB.com | author=David Adler | date=August 19, 2020 | accessdate=August 20, 2020 | archive-date=2020-08-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820092245/https://www.mlb.com/tigers/news/casey-mize-dane-dunning-debut-history | dead-url=no }}</ref>主投4.1局送出7次三振，失3分無關勝敗。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.mlb.com/news/casey-mize-strikes-out-7-in-mlb-debut |title=A-Mize-ing! Casey fans 7, walks 0 in debut |work=MLB.com |last=Beck |first=Jason |date=August 19, 2020 |accessdate=August 20, 2020 |archive-date=2020-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200822220423/https://www.mlb.com/news/casey-mize-strikes-out-7-in-mlb-debut |dead-url=no }}</ref>9月11日，麥茲投出5局的無安打，不過到了第6局破功。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.detroitnews.com/story/sports/mlb/tigers/2020/09/11/tigers-casey-mize-pitching-no-hitter-through-five-innings-vs-white-sox/5773733002/ |title=White Sox's Yolmer Sanchez ends Casey Mize's bid for no-hitter with double in the 6th |newspaper=[[The_Detroit_News|The Detroit News]] |date=September 11, 2020 |access-date=September 11, 2020 |archive-date=2020-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920204732/https://www.detroitnews.com/story/sports/mlb/tigers/2020/09/11/tigers-casey-mize-pitching-no-hitter-through-five-innings-vs-white-sox/5773733002/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>該年他在老虎隊先發7場，拿下0勝3敗，防禦率6.99。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mlb.com/player/casey-mize-663554 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-10-31 |archive-date=2020-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217173153/https://www.mlb.com/player/casey-mize-663554 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2021年4月12日，麥茲拿下大聯盟首勝。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.freep.com/story/sports/mlb/tigers/2021/03/26/detroit-tigers-casey-mize-mlb-roster-michael-fulmer/7006335002/ |title=Detroit Tigers' Casey Mize impresses for first MLB win in 6-2 victory over Houston Astros |last=Petzold |first=Evan |website=freep.com |date=April 12, 2021 |access-date=April 13, 2021 |archive-date=2021-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210507183738/https://www.freep.com/story/sports/mlb/tigers/2021/03/26/detroit-tigers-casey-mize-mlb-roster-michael-fulmer/7006335002/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>8月24日，麥茲首度上場打擊，並在滿壘獲得保送，拿下生涯首分打點。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.mlb.com/news/casey-mize-earns-first-career-rbi-in-tigers-win?game_pk=632781 |title=Tigers soaking up good vibes in recent run |last=Harris |first=Joe |website=MLB.com |date=August 24, 2021 |access-date=August 25, 2021 |archive-date=2022-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220403055526/https://www.mlb.com/news/casey-mize-earns-first-career-rbi-in-tigers-win?game_pk=632781 |dead-url=no }}</ref>整季他投出7勝9敗，防禦率3.71。

